[
  {
    "unit_id": "U0144",
    "index": 144,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "heading",
    "text": "## 3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 145,
    "line_end": 145,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0145",
    "index": 145,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "烈日当空，长安城外村口集市已从晨间的热闹转为下午的喧",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 146,
    "line_end": 146,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0146",
    "index": 146,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "嚣，尘土飞扬中混着汗臭和烤饼的焦香，摊贩们的吆喝声如",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 147,
    "line_end": 147,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0147",
    "index": 147,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "浪潮般起伏。林辰正收着最后几枚铜钱，布袋沉甸甸的凉意",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 148,
    "line_end": 148,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0148",
    "index": 148,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "渗入手心，阿翠在旁帮着打包肥皂块，布裙下腰肢微弯，汗",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 149,
    "line_end": 149,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0149",
    "index": 149,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "珠顺着她清秀的脖颈滑落，隐现一丝细瘦曲线。她低头时，",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 150,
    "line_end": 150,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0150",
    "index": 150,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "眼神瞥向林辰，坚强中透着依赖，空气中那缕草木清香若有",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 151,
    "line_end": 151,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0151",
    "index": 151,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "若无地缠绕，让他心头一紧——这丫头，昨夜还为他熬粥，",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 152,
    "line_end": 152,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0152",
    "index": 152,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "今天又守摊，老子得快点逆袭，省得她总这么操心。",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 153,
    "line_end": 153,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0153",
    "index": 153,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "正爽着，远处马蹄叩击地面，急促如鼓点，尘土中挤出一群",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 154,
    "line_end": 154,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0154",
    "index": 154,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "彪悍家丁，为首是个肥硕身影，赵霸那张油腻脸在阳光下闪",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 155,
    "line_end": 155,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0155",
    "index": 155,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "着汗光，锦袍裹着啤酒肚，腰间还别着根镶银鞭子。他眯眼",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 156,
    "line_end": 156,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0156",
    "index": 156,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "锁定林辰的摊位，嘴角勾起嚣张弧度，身后七八个家丁挥舞",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 157,
    "line_end": 157,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0157",
    "index": 157,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "棍棒，粗鲁叫骂声炸开，“小子，听说你卖的盐和肥皂挺邪",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 158,
    "line_end": 158,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0158",
    "index": 158,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "门？乖乖交出秘方，饶你不死！”赵霸的声音嗡嗡如猪哼，眼",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 159,
    "line_end": 159,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0159",
    "index": 159,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "神满是欺软怕硬的得意，心理盘算着抢了这玩意儿，就能垄",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 160,
    "line_end": 160,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0160",
    "index": 160,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "断村里生意，顺带踩扁这个乞丐新人。",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 161,
    "line_end": 161,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0161",
    "index": 161,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "林辰冷笑，现代智商瞬间上线，古人这智商，就跟幼儿园小",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 162,
    "line_end": 162,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0162",
    "index": 162,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "孩似的。他上前一步，将阿翠拉到身后，手掌不经意碰上她",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 163,
    "line_end": 163,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0163",
    "index": 163,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "腰间布料，粗粝触感中带着一丝颤动，她身子微僵，却没",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 164,
    "line_end": 164,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0164",
    "index": 164,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "退，眼神中闪过隐忍的坚强。“赵霸是吧？肥硕如猪还想抢东",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 165,
    "line_end": 165,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0165",
    "index": 165,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "西，就这智商也配当村霸？老子大学时候抓小偷都比你专",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 166,
    "line_end": 166,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0166",
    "index": 166,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "业。”林辰毒舌吐出，声音果断带刺，围观农妇们倒吸凉气，",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 167,
    "line_end": 167,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0167",
    "index": 167,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "议论声如潮水涌起。",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 168,
    "line_end": 168,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0168",
    "index": 168,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "赵霸脸涨红，猪肝色般扭曲，鞭子一挥，“小子找死！上，给",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 169,
    "line_end": 169,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0169",
    "index": 169,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "我打残他！”家丁群起而攻，棍棒呼啸，尘土中汗臭扑鼻。林",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 170,
    "line_end": 170,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0170",
    "index": 170,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "辰眼神锋芒一闪，军体拳基础融合现代格斗，迅捷侧身避开",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 171,
    "line_end": 171,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0171",
    "index": 171,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "第一棍，泥土湿滑踩得他小腿一紧，拳头直击领头家丁胸",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 172,
    "line_end": 172,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0172",
    "index": 172,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "膛，闷响如骨裂，热血喷溅的咸涩味弥漫空气。那家丁扑通",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 173,
    "line_end": 173,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0173",
    "index": 173,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "倒地，粗臂上的汗珠甩出，砸起一地尘灰。林辰不退反进，",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 174,
    "line_end": 174,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0174",
    "index": 174,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "肘击第二人肩头，钝响伴着痛呼，阳光下他小麦色肌肤泛起",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 175,
    "line_end": 175,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0175",
    "index": 175,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "薄汗，触感如铁般坚硬，战袍般的破布紧贴身躯，勾勒出精",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 176,
    "line_end": 176,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0176",
    "index": 176,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "壮线条。",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 177,
    "line_end": 177,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0177",
    "index": 177,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "dialogue",
    "text": "“就这？老子军训时都打得更猛！”林辰吐槽，脚下一扫，绊",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 178,
    "line_end": 178,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0178",
    "index": 178,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "倒第三个，棍子脱手飞出，砸中赵霸脚边。家丁们慌了，围",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 179,
    "line_end": 179,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0179",
    "index": 179,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "攻转为乱打，棍风带起尘土迷眼，林辰抓起陶罐护胸，另一",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 180,
    "line_end": 180,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0180",
    "index": 180,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "手抡圆，拳风呼啸间撂倒两人，骨头摩擦的闷响混着哀嚎，",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 181,
    "line_end": 181,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0181",
    "index": 181,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "空气中血腥铁锈味渐浓。阿翠虽恐惧，脸色苍白中却坚定上",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 182,
    "line_end": 182,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0182",
    "index": 182,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "action",
    "text": "前，递过把菜刀，刀刃反射阳光的寒光映照她隐忍的眼神，",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 183,
    "line_end": 183,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0183",
    "index": 183,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "dialogue",
    "text": "“辰哥，小心！”她声音软糯，布裙在风中微荡，腰间的曲线",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 184,
    "line_end": 184,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0184",
    "index": 184,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "隐现压迫感，两人间默契如丝线拉扯，从初步互助向情感依",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 185,
    "line_end": 185,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0185",
    "index": 185,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "action",
    "text": "恋递进。",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 186,
    "line_end": 186,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0186",
    "index": 186,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "赵霸见势不妙，鞭子抖得像筛糠，肥硕身躯后退，脸色煞白",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 187,
    "line_end": 187,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0187",
    "index": 187,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "dialogue",
    "text": "中带着恐惧，“误会！小子，有话好说……”他勉强赔礼，声",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 188,
    "line_end": 188,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0188",
    "index": 188,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "音颤颤，家丁们狼狈爬起，灰头土脸退散。村民们爆发出欢",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 189,
    "line_end": 189,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0189",
    "index": 189,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "dialogue",
    "text": "呼，掌声雷动如潮，“林小子威武！赵霸这回栽了！”林辰拍",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 190,
    "line_end": 190,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0190",
    "index": 190,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "拍手，铜钱袋更沉了，他瞥向阿翠，护短的本能让他心头一",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 191,
    "line_end": 191,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0191",
    "index": 191,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "暖——谁敢动她，老子灭他满门。",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 192,
    "line_end": 192,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0192",
    "index": 192,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "action",
    "text": "收摊后，林辰揽着布匹和阿翠往村边走，夕阳拉长影子，尘",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 193,
    "line_end": 193,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0193",
    "index": 193,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "土渐息。阿翠低头擦拭他手背的汗渍，指尖轻柔如仪式，温",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 194,
    "line_end": 194,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0194",
    "index": 194,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "热触感中透出感激，“辰哥，你……真厉害。赵霸平时横行霸",
    "scene_name": "3. 打脸村霸赵霸",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 195,
    "line_end": 195,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0195",
    "index": 195,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "道，从没人敢惹。”她眼神坚强中藏依赖，红晕爬上脸颊，两",
